  "body": "The value of `logIndex` returned by `eth_getReceipt` disagrees with both Parity and Geth.  For both of those clients, they report the index of the log IN THE BLOCK. TurboGeth reports the index of the log IN THE TRANSACTION.\r\n\r\nParity adds a new field (`transactionLogIndex`) which shows the index of the log in the transaction.\r\n\r\nThis curl command:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -s --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getTransactionReceipt\",\"params\":[\"0x6afbe0f0ea3613edd6b84b71260836c03bddce81604f05c81a070cd671d3d765\"],\"id\":\"1\"}' -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -X POST localhost:8545\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe image explains more easily:\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5417918/92656063-662ba380-f2c0-11ea-9269-dcad43c9ca90.png)\r\n",
